{"tid":2074210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"終於知道點解聶德權話香港公務員係國家公務人員...","createTime":"2020-06-22T02:44:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T03:07:06.000Z","uid":7542,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1b29194d68d7b399b8d0ae53550db417e6fcecc3","tid":2074210,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T02:44:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/17qa0vy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F17qa0vy.png&h=1210c4cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">啱啱中國立多咗條法規...</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>據中共黨媒新華社消息，中共人大常委會第十九次會議在6月20日通過了所謂的《中華人民共和國公職人員政務處分法》，新華社的解讀文章聲言要解決&ldquo;政紀不適用， 黨紀管不了&rdquo;問題(圖1)，<strong><em>並將政務處分範圍從黨政機關公務員擴大到國企管理人員、公辦教科文衛體單位管理人員</em></strong>(圖2)，似乎該法的頒布只是為了加強對公職人員 的監督。<br />\n 而本社小編在翻查新華社公佈的該法條文時發現，該法&ldquo;違法行為及其適用的政務處分&rdquo;一章一開始就列舉的懲罰最嚴重的是政治類罪名(圖3)，包括 <strong><em>發表反共言論、參與遊行示威、參與&ldquo;非法組織與活動&rdquo;、&ldquo;挑撥破壞民族關係及參加民族分裂活動&rdquo;、&ldquo;利用宗教活動破壞民族團結和社會穩定&rdquo;，並規定對&ldquo;策劃者、組織者和 骨幹分子&rdquo;直接開除，而公開發表和中共腔調不一致的文章、演說、宣言、聲明也會予以開除。</em></strong></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要清算罷工嘅公務員？法理基礎都準備埋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oEV6yPn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoEV6yPn.jpg&h=81a38ea1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7G93A2G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7G93A2G.jpg&h=31b4a3e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pVqqPnH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpVqqPnH.jpg&h=4130aabf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d7a067459f1b09b80bf50b2a3d7f8a285823b75c","tid":2074210,"uid":7542,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-0